channel.title: Different Color Gameframes
channel.description:
Well I fiddled with my image program and decided to recolour my gameframe to a few different colors.
This pack contains the normal gameframe, red gameframe, blue gameframe, and green gameframe.
If you would like another color for this gameframe, just let me know I'll update it.
Download link: [url=http://uppit.com/v/7E8A4BXF]http://uppit.com/v/7E8A4BXF[/url]
Regular: [IMG]http://i38.tinypic.com/t6te3c.jpg[/img]
Blue Gameframe: [IMG]http://i34.tinypic.com/25qym9s.jpg[/img]
